trans-unit.source: Plays a media file.
trans-unit.target: Spiller media-fil.

trans-unit.source: If the media is a video file, the VideoDrawing draws it to the specified rectangle.
trans-unit.target: Hvis mediet er en video fil, tegner VideoDrawing den angitte rektangel.

trans-unit.source: Although you can declare an instance of this class in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], you cannot load and play its media without using code, because of the dependency on the <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer> class and in particular the <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Open%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Play%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Selv om du kan angi en forekomst av denne klassen i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], du kan ikke laste inn og spille mediet uten å bruke kode, på grunn av avhengigheten på den <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer>klassen og spesielt den <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Open%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Play%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Play%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer.Open%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaPlayer>

trans-unit.source: To play media in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] only, use a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
trans-unit.target: Å spille media i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] , bruker <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>

trans-unit.source: Despite its name, a VideoDrawing can be used to play audio.
trans-unit.target: Til tross for navnet, kan en VideoDrawing brukes til å spille lyd.

trans-unit.source: **Performance Note:** A VideoDrawing provides fewer features then an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>: VideoDrawing does not support layout, input, or focus.
trans-unit.target: **Obs! ytelse** en VideoDrawing inneholder færre funksjoner og deretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>: VideoDrawing støtter ikke oppsett, inndata eller fokus.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>

trans-unit.source: However, because it does not support these features, VideoDrawing provides performance benefits making them ideal for describing backgrounds, clip art, and for low-level drawing with <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual> objects.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid fordi den ikke støtter disse funksjonene, VideoDrawing gir ytelsesfordeler slik at de ideelle for som beskriver spillerbakgrunner, klipp art og lavt nivå tegning med <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>

trans-unit.source: See [Drawing Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for more information.
trans-unit.target: Se [tegning oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for mer informasjon.

trans-unit.source: An VideoDrawing is a type of <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> object and therefore can be frozen to improve performance.
trans-unit.target: En VideoDrawing er en type <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>objekt, og derfor kan være låst for å forbedre ytelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>

trans-unit.source: For information about <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> features, such as freezing and cloning, see the [Freezable Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>Funksjoner, for eksempel fryse og kloning, kan du se den [oversikt over Freezable](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>
